pARTykelir project

pARTykelir ( party & colors) pesta warna in Bahasa (indonesia language)

the pARTykelir project is belong to me.  singpentinkhappy NFT is a completely new Art with conceptual story & message.  while this partykelir project is my old experimental abstract vector art that I recomposed to the new arts. The purpose of this project is to prevent the irresponsible actions of scammers who acknowledge my work as theirs.  that's why I made my old work NFT.
